PeppyPenguin.rulesText:
At the start of Action Time,
if this Penguin has vibe 6 or greater,
boost its vibe by 6 for the rest of this Cycle.

BizmoPhDCandidate.rulesText:
When this Penguin enters the huddle,
if you have no cards in your deck,
you win the game.

TheEndoftheRainbow.rulesText:
At the start of Action Time,
if your huddle contains a Penguin of each color,
draw a card.
